HEADWORD: Impennate
<hw>Im*pen"nate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Characterized by short wings covered with feathers resembling
scales, as the penguins.</def> -- <def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>One of the
Impennes.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
